    description: "<ul>\n<li>parameters:<ul>\n<li><code>list</code>: list</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>result: list</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"language-feel\">distinct values([1,2,3,2,1])\n// [1,2,3]\n</code></pre>\n"
